        <item>
            <title>1.8.2</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 10:06:43 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>63</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.2</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Added</strong></p><ul><li>📄 Added `.xls` support in document analysis and extraction flows</li><li>📬 Added automated Telegram metrics digests for release monitoring</li></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>⚡ Improved failed-processing retry flow and error visibility</li><li>📊 Improved metrics digest calculations and reporting consistency</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>🛡️ Hardened Paddle webhook signature validation and retry handling</li><li>🩹 Reduced noisy monitoring/Sentry events in backend processing</li></ul>
]]></description>
